<h3>Features and Traits</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Constructed Resilience:</strong> Ossivar doesn’t require air, food, drink, or sleep. He has advantage on saving throws against being poisoned and is immune to disease.</li>
<li><strong>Darkvision:</strong> Ossivar can see in dim light within 60 feet as if it were bright light, and in darkness as if it were dim light.</li>
<li><strong>Shattered Memories:</strong> Ossivar can tap into the voices of his foundational shards for guidance and has advantage on History checks related to ancient crafting techniques and lost knowledge.</li>
<li><strong>Magic Resistance:</strong> He has advantage on saving throws against spells.</li>
<li><strong>Spellcasting (Artificer):</strong> Ossivar can cast spells using Intelligence as his spellcasting ability.</li>
</ol>
<h3>Spellcasting</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Cantrips (2):</strong> Mending, Guidance</li>
<li><strong>1st Level Spells (2 prepared slots):</strong> Cure Wounds (flavored as reanimating bones), Armor of Agathys</li>
</ul>
